           );

my $legendLocal = "
Subscription:                Novell product which customer may be entitled to 
                             receive patches, updates or technical support 
                             during the period covered by the subscription.
Locally Registered Machines: the registered machines connected to the SMT 
                             with access to patches, updates or technical 
                             support.
